# I will explian overhang concept first.
# overhang 0%:
# ____     upper layer
# ____     lower layer
# overhang 25%:
# ____    upper layer
#  ____   lower layer
# overhang 50%:
# ____      upper layer
#    ____   lower layer
# overhang 75%
# ____        upper layer
#      ____   lower layer
# overhang 100%
# ____          upper layer
#        ____   lower layer
